data.description: Final Price Drop!!! Amazing Opportunity to Own this 3BR/2BA SFH w/ Oversized 600 Sq. Ft. Detached Garage (Many uses as additional space Football Game Day/Kids Hangout/Workshop/Yoga Studio). Home sits on 2 lots & was remodeled in 2019. You will love the Oversized Kitchen w/ Granite Counter Tops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Tile Flooring & Eat-In Area. Main Level includes Primary Bedroom w/ a Full En-Suite, 2nd Bedroom, Hallway Full BA & Vinyl Plank Flooring in Family Room. Upstairs you will find an Oversized Bedroom w/ Walk-In Attic. Additional features: Solar Panel & Water Treatment System Paid in Full at Closing at listed price or Buyer(s) may be eligible to qualify for a separate loan to finance both, reach out for more info. Fenced Back Yard, Bedrooms w/ Carpet, Front Porch & Back Deck. Architectural Roof, HVAC & Plumbing all new in 2014. (Home/Garage/Appliances are selling As-Is, Seller will make no repairs)
